    "None of the on articles on the module's suggested reading list were provided by GPT4.",
    "These findings concur with a systematic review of ChatGPT undertaken by Singh and Singh (2023, pp. 193-212) which determined that, whilst ChatGPT generated content is remarkable, it is not always good.",
